parameters: 女戦士だけ居るエンド

Levia: "Hmm, I heard there was an intruder, but I
never imagined it would be you..."

Levia: "So you got your hands on a good weapon and
thought you'd rebel against your master, huh?"

Ruth: "Hmph, enjoy talking big while you still
can, yeah?"

Levia: "Fufufu... Well, alright. I'll entertain
you."
Levia: "Make sure you at least amuse me a little."
Levia: "Come on, come on, entertain me more."
この辺マップチップで攻防
Ruth: (Damn it! Is Reeza's power not enough?!)

Levia: "Flames of hell, devour everything! Hell
Flame!!"

Levia: "Ahahaha! You thought you could do
something with that level of effort?"

Levia: "But well, thanks to you bringing her here,
you've saved me some trouble~"

Levia: "Traitors need to be punished, don't
they~♪"

Ruth: "P-Please, I'll do anything, just spare my
life..."
Levia: "Oh my, what brings you here?"

Ruth: "I have completed the mission and have come
to report."

Levia: "Ah, yes, yes, the female warrior from that
village!"

Levia: "I never thought you'd make it back
alive..."

Levia: "Well, you must be tired. You may stand
down."

Levia: "Do you have a complaint? If you're done
with your tasks, then get out of my sight quickly,
will you?"

Ruth: (What the hell, so I get nothing in
return...)

Ruth: (Maybe I should have staged a coup or
something...)
女戦士と魔術師が居るエンド

Levia: "Hmm, I heard reports of an intruder, but I
never imagined it would be you..."

Levia: "So you got your hands on a nice weapon and
thought you'd rebel against your master, huh?"

Ruth: "Hmph, enjoy your mocking while you can, it
won't last long!"

Levia: "Hehehe... Well, alright. I'll entertain
you."
Levia: "I'm busy, so let's make this quick!"

Levia: "Flames of hell, consume everything! Hell
Flame!!"
Levia: "Oh... You can block my flames..."

Cyan: "...I will stop your magic with all my
might."

Levia: "Hehehe... You're cute. But don't think
that just because you blocked my magic, you can
defeat me!"
Levia: "Oh, are you my next opponent?"
Reeza: "I will be the one to defeat you!"

Levia: "You're quite skilled, just as the rumors
say. But that's not enough to defeat me."
Cyan: "Icicle Lance, pierce through my enemies!"

Levia: "Too bad♪ My magic doesn't work on you, but
your magic doesn't work on me either."
Levia: "Come on, what's wrong? Entertain me more!"

Ruth: "You guys! I'm leaving this to you, I'm
getting out of here!"

Levia: "Traitors need to be punished, don't
they~♪"

Ruth: "P-Please... I'll do anything, just spare my
life..."

Levia: "Really? If you listen to what I say, then
I'll spare your life."

Levia: "I've taken a liking to these girls♪ So,
could you order them to always listen to what I
say from now on?"
Ruth: "If I do that, will you really spare me?"
And so, I was spared from losing my life...
However, in exchange, I was thrown into prison...

I thought about using the girls to escape, but it
seems magic is sealed within the prison walls, and
I could no longer control them...

However, as long as I live, the order for them to
obey Levia remains in effect.

As long as Levia continues to use them, she can't
afford to let me die, so my meals are brought
regularly.

I have no freedom, but at least my safety is
guaranteed...

Ruth: "(A weakling like me could die at any time,
so for now, I should be content with this
situation.)"

I don't know how long I'll be able to live, but as
long as I'm alive, that's how I've decided to
spend my days...

ago? Eh, Levia?"

to dieeeeeeeeee!"

Levia: "Well then, Ruth... goodbye... Hell
Flame!!"
